title: #TOURNOTES: GOLDEN GOLDIES
description: The contest may have finished, but the fun certainly hasn't. Between a grom-judged heat between John John and Kolohe, to a game of footy between Carissa Moore and family, to pumping Snapper the Gold Coast isn't a bad place hang post-comp. See more from the Hurley crew at http://hurley.com/athletes
